      <section>
         <sectiondiv>
            <p>The UPS system can be placed up against the
wall. Leave a distance of 100 mm (4 in) between the UPS and the wall.</p>
            <note>Clearance dimensions are published for airflow only. Consult
with the local safety codes and standards for additional requirements
in your local area.</note>
